metadata.name: CacheConcern #cache_collection when given a collection of statuses correctly updates with new interactions

sql_query.sql: SELECT "statuses"."id", "statuses"."updated_at" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."account_id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
SELECT "media_attachments".* FROM "media_attachments" WHERE "media_attachments"."status_id" = $1 ORDER BY "media_attachments"."id" ASC

SELECT a.attname
  FROM (
         SELECT indrelid, indkey, generate_subscripts(indkey, 1) idx
           FROM pg_index
          WHERE indrelid = '"statuses_tags"'::regclass
            AND indisprimary
       ) i
  JOIN pg_attribute a
    ON a.attrelid = i.indrelid
   AND a.attnum = i.indkey[i.idx]
 ORDER BY i.idx

SELECT a.attname
  FROM (
         SELECT indrelid, indkey, generate_subscripts(indkey, 1) idx
           FROM pg_index
          WHERE indrelid = '"preview_cards_statuses"'::regclass
            AND indisprimary
       ) i
  JOIN pg_attribute a
    ON a.attrelid = i.indrelid
   AND a.attnum = i.indkey[i.idx]
 ORDER BY i.idx
